        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Production volume is expressed in kg. About 15,531,400 culms of Guadua Angustifolia Kunt were harvested in Ecuador in 2022 on approximately 15,000 ha (INBAR 2015). A culm weights about 30 kg (Fabian Moreno, project manager INBAR Ecuador) and its density is about 118.84 kg/m3 

Reference: 
INBAR (2015) ESTUDIO DE LA CADENA DESDE LA PRODUCCIÓN AL CONSUMO DEL BAMBÚ EN ECUADOR CON ÉNFASIS EN LA ESPECIE Guadua angustifolia
https://bambuecuador.files.wordpress.com/2018/01/2015-estudio-de-la-cadena-desde-la-producciocc81n-al-consumo-del-bmabucc81-en-ecuador.pdf</productionVolumeComment>
